ZH: 我们需要测量一下这个房间的面积。
EN: We need to measure the area of this room.

ZH: 你可以拿尺子来测量一下这个桌子的长度吗？
EN: Can you use a ruler to measure the length of this table?

ZH: 这个工具可以帮助我们测量温度。
EN: This tool can help us measure temperature.

ZH: 在建筑设计中，经常需要测量各种尺寸。
EN: In architectural design, it is often necessary to measure various dimensions.

ZH: 科学家们用仪器测量了地震的强度。
EN: Scientists measured the intensity of the earthquake using instruments.

ZH: 他们使用雷达来测量距离。
EN: They used radar to measure the distance.

ZH: 工程师正在测量该建筑物的结构强度。
EN: Engineers are measuring the structural strength of the building.

ZH: 你可以用体重秤来测量自己的体重。
EN: You can use a scale to measure your weight.

ZH: 妇科医生使用超声波来测量孕妇的腹围。
EN: Gynecologists use ultrasound to measure the abdominal circumference of pregnant women.

ZH: 海洋学家使用声纳来测量海底深度。
EN: Oceanographers use sonar to measure the depth of the seabed.

