EN: Workers measured the height and width of the building.

ZH: 这个尺子可以用来测量体积。
EN: This ruler can be used to measure volume.

ZH: 这是一项关于心脏健康的实验，需要测量血压和心率。
EN: This is an experiment on heart health, which requires measuring blood pressure and heart rate.

ZH: 他们利用卫星测量了地球的准确尺寸。
EN: They used satellites to measure the precise size of the Earth.

ZH: 医生可以用血液检测来测量某些疾病的指标。
EN: Doctors can use blood tests to measure certain indicators of diseases.

ZH: 进行实验前，我们需要测量所需的材料。
EN: Before conducting the experiment, we need to measure the required materials.

ZH: 我们正在测量空气中的气体浓度。
EN: We are measuring the concentration of gases in the air.

ZH: 班里每个学生都需要接受身高和体重的测量。
EN: Every student in the class needs to undergo height and weight measurements.
